WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:03.840
Accidents often happen before you notice them.

00:03.840 --> 00:07.760
You could fall when you go down the stairs at school.

00:07.760 --> 00:10.840
It's quite dangerous in the kitchen at home,

00:10.840 --> 00:14.480
because broken glass or knives can cut you.

00:14.480 --> 00:18.680
And moving heavy furniture is dangerous too.

00:18.680 --> 00:22.680
You could drop it and hurt your foot.

